The Deliveries Setup page is the central configuration point for the EOS FOOD Deliveries module. It is a single setup page that holds all the module's options.

---

## Configuration Sections

### 1. Number Series (Numerations)

Configure the number series used for automatic document numbering:

| Field | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| **Land Mapping Nos.** | Specifies the number series used to assign unique identifiers to land mapping records. |
| **Disciplinary Nos.** | Specifies the number series used to assign unique identifiers to disciplinary records. |
| **Deliveries Receipt Nos.** | Specifies the number series used to assign unique identifiers to deliveries receipt documents. |
| **Posted Deliveries Receipt Nos.** | Specifies the number series used to assign unique identifiers to posted deliveries receipt documents. |

### 2. Reason Codes

Configure default reason codes used when creating delivery orders:

| Field | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| **Deliveries Reason Code** | Specifies the default reason code applied to delivery orders. |
| **Own Prod. Deliv. Reason Code** | Specifies the default reason code applied to own production delivery orders. |

### 3. Processing

Configure document creation behavior:

| Field | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| **Deliveries Document Type** | Specifies the default purchase document type (Order or Blanket Order) created when generating delivery orders from land mappings. |
| **Deliv. Document Lines Grouping** | Specifies how purchase document lines are grouped when creating delivery orders from land mappings. |
| **Company Vendor No.** | Specifies the vendor number representing the company itself, used for own production deliveries. |

### 4. Deliveries Receipts

| Field | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| **Enable Deliv. Rcpt. Status Mgt** | Specifies whether the status management workflow is enabled for deliveries receipts, allowing status transitions before posting. |

---

## Setup Checklist

Before using the module, ensure the following are configured:

- [ ] All four number series are assigned
- [ ] Deliveries Reason Code is set
- [ ] Own Prod. Deliv. Reason Code is set (if using own production)
- [ ] Company Vendor No. is set (if using own production deliveries)
- [ ] Deliveries Document Type is selected (Order or Blanket Order)
- [ ] Lines Grouping method is selected
- [ ] Status Management is enabled/disabled per business requirements
